data.description: This BEAUTIFUL home needs a new owner! 4 bedroom 2 bath home is turn-key and ready for you to move in. Open floor plan with lots of natural light. Enjoy nature at it's best with fruit trees surrounding a HUGE lot! Property has a wood burning stove, redwood deck with a covered patio and stamped concrete. This Two-acre property is completely fenced, ready for all your toys, RVs, horses you name it! Schedule your viewing appointment ASAP!
